---
title: Booking Process - Activity Diagram
---
flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Select Passenger from dropdown]
    B --> C[Select Train from dropdown]
    C --> D{Is train Active?}
    D -->|No| E[Display error: Train not active]
    E --> Z([End])
    D -->|Yes| F[Enter travel date and seat count]
    F --> G[Click Book Ticket]
    G --> H{Seat count > 0?}
    H -->|No| I[Display error: Must be at least 1]
    I --> Z
    H -->|Yes| J{Enough seats available?}
    J -->|No| K[Display error: Not enough seats]
    K --> Z
    J -->|Yes| L{Travel date provided?}
    L -->|No| M[Display error: Date required]
    M --> Z
    L -->|Yes| N[Calculate total price]
    N --> O[Create Reservation - CONFIRMED]
    O --> P[Deduct seats from train]
    P --> Q[Save to DataStore]
    Q --> R[Display booking confirmation]
    R --> S[Refresh tables and dropdowns]
    S --> Z

    style A fill:#009688,color:#fff
    style Z fill:#dc3545,color:#fff
    style D fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style H fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style J fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style L fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style O fill:#19376d,color:#fff
    style R fill:#28a745,color:#fff
